        <updateDate>2018-12-07T21:53:04Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>No Arms Sales to Iran Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits military assistance or military export licenses from being provided to a country that engages in U.N.-restricted arms transfers to or activity with Iran.</p> <p>The President may waive such prohibitions if in the U.S. national interest.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
